Successor to the Divine Dragon, awoken from a long sleep. Summons Emblems to lead the world to peace.

The staunch and loyal crown prince of Firene. He trains constantly to strengthen his constitution.

Princess Céline's retainer. A smiling, refined gentleman who loves tea.
A thief encountered in a mountain settlement. She keeps a tight lid on the details of her past.

Prince Diamant's retainer. Has a boundless enthusiasm for legends and adventure.

A warrior from Brodia. She is a dauntless and determined seeker of truth.

The Fell Dragon King. A wicked creature who wields immense dark power.
The kind queen of Firene. A gentle soul who wishes for a world without strife or conflict.
The brave king of Brodia. A powerful and proud warrior, he prizes honor on the battlefield.
The cunning king of Elusia. Worships the Fell Dragon and schemes for the advancement of his country.
